==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Reeve
<hw>Reeve</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Rove</conjf> <pr>(r⟦omac⟧v)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Reeving</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[Cf. D. <ets>reven</ets>. See
