==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Reeve
<hw>Reeve</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>reve</ets>, AS.
<ets>ger⟦emac⟧fa</ets>. Cf. <er>Sheriff</er>.]</ety> <def>An officer,
steward, bailiff, or governor; -- used chiefly in compounds; <as>as,
